/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a bustling street scene in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a sense of being in the midst of the action. The sky above is a clear blue, providing a vibrant backdrop to the urban landscape below. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, interspersed with trees that add a touch of greenery to the concrete jungle. Cars of different colors are scattered across the road, hinting at the busy traffic typical of city life. Overhead, power lines crisscross against the sky, a common sight in many urban areas. The image is taken from a low angle, which emphasizes the height of the buildings and gives a sense of scale to the scene.
